( 1, 'targnon01', 9, 'In the picture you can see the destroyed Panther 211 of Kampfgruppe Peiper. Another tank and ambulance truck can also be seen on the left side.\nOn the 19th of December in the afternoon, Kampfgruppe Peiper wanted to continuo their march, but met with 12 tanks of the American 743th Tank Battalion. This would be the fursthest their advance would get. They would pull back to Stoumont.', '50.41727829', '5.76433754', 'Targnon', 1, '1944-12-20', 1, '', 1, '2020-12-05 21:38:09', '2020-08-31 21:06:27'),
