( 1, 'malmedy02', 9, 'Ersatz Panther B-10 Panther.\nSince the  Ersatz Panther did not have a cover on the turret, you needed to looked out to get bearings. This one was commanded by Lt Gerstenschlager. He was hit in the head, while looking over the side of the turret. When the Panther came under heavy fire from US troops,  the driver tried to escape, and put it in reverce, driving the Panther partially into Café Du Rocher de Falize in La Falize. The rest of the crew panned and left the Panther.', '50.41414642', '6.00791168', 'Malmedy', 1, '1945-07-15', 1, '', 1, '2020-12-05 20:46:10', '2020-09-01 17:19:55'),
